com.cognifide.slice.mapper.api.processor

Interface PriorityFieldProcessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FieldProcessor, PriorityProcessor

    public interface PriorityFieldProcessor
extends FieldProcessor, PriorityProcessor
    Its purpose is to add a possibility to register custom processors with defined priority. Objects of this class should be registered with Guice's multibindings.
    The priority parameter is used to sort processors. Processors with higher priority will take precedence over those with lower prioroty. Notice that all PriorityFieldProcessors always take precedence over any other FieldProcessors.
    Author:
    maciej.dybek
